{File:TLT_IS.txt  Index:18  Index Date:20160510  PL:83.33%  PS:16.67%  Trades:6  CL:1}

IF HIGH OF 0 BARS AGO > HIGH OF 1 BARS AGO
AND HIGH OF 1 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 0 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 0 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 1 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 1 BARS AGO > HIGH OF 2 BARS AGO
AND HIGH OF 2 BARS AGO > LOW OF 0 BARS AGO
AND LOW OF 0 BARS AGO > LOW OF 1 BARS AGO
AND LOW OF 1 BARS AGO > LOW OF 2 BARS AGO
THEN BUY NEXT BAR ON THE OPEN WITH
PROFIT TARGET AT ENTRY PRICE + 0.834493 %
AND STOP LOSS AT ENTRY PRICE - 0.735933 %
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
